==English==

===Noun===
'''dimple''' (''plural:'' '''dimples''')

# a small [[depression]]
#: ''The accident created a '''dimple''' in the hood of the car.''
# small [[depression]] on the [[skin]], especially on the [[face]] near the corners of the [[mouth]]
#: ''You have very cute '''dimples'''.''

