===Verb===
'''to dimple''' ('''dimples''', '''dimpled''', '''dimpling''')

# {{italbrac|transitive}} To create a dimple in.
#: ''The hailstorm '''dimpled''' the roof of our car.'' 
# {{intransitive}} To create a dimple by [[smiling]].

